{"tid":469171,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"政府工 vs 私人工","createTime":"2017-11-15T05:15:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T05:13:59.000Z","uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7693a139d10e8e18a0aeca77b04e6797f77d6b76","tid":469171,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T05:15:09.000Z","msg":"工作經驗值：2年<br />\n年齡：24<br />\n<br />\n私人工 - 人工28k, 18日假有雙糧花紅<br />\n- 銀行office工，非sales唔洗跑數<br />\n- 係同類工種已建立一定經驗知識同人脈<br />\n- 暫時需求大 跳槽加薪容易 第日會點就難講<br />\n- 唔知長遠黎講同類工種會唔會有痿縮危機<br />\n- 私人工話炒就炒<br />\n<br />\n政府工 - 人工28k (mps pt15) (general grade, 非專業職系) <br />\n- officer位 每2年左右轉一次posting<br />\n- 穩定！人到中年唔會俾人炒<br />\n- 過probat後政府供15%mpf 退休生活有保障<br />\n- 人工加幅冇fantasy可言 計埋升職預計30歲時人工大約等同現時嘅55k - 67k, 之後都未必會有大增 除非有幸晉身高級公務員(機會有 但不算太大) <br />\n- 做耐左就可能轉唔返出私人市場，流動性低<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n工作壓力係點就好難講 始終而家政府工都唔見得舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家會點選擇"},{"pid":"a5ee8f06bdcd826ea54a47c693b4615c87410470","tid":469171,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T05:15:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d9fe59692ad5fa6222411e806624ce6fb962341","tid":469171,"uid":116788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T05:16:45.000Z","msg":"學歷?"},{"pid":"d4f654f4c3e0571683b183c1b31db28f4fbf7270","tid":469171,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T05:17:02.000Z","msg":"我就揀私人<br />\n樓主介紹份政府俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c41daa5440b74b8663e6b69ec9682a29603c3048","tid":469171,"uid":17718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T05:17:42.000Z","msg":"政府"},{"pid":"3d552a71eea9b56fb9dd3d1d19e83e36cea1caf8","tid":469171,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T05:18:29.000Z","